Package: wifi-honey
Version: 1.1.1
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: NeosLab <contact@neoslab.com>
Description:  In the case of WPA/WPA2, by running airodump-ng along side this you also end up capturing the first two packets of the four way handshake and so can attempt to crack the key with either aircrack-ng or cowpatty.
